{"tid":2421034,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府嘅高地價政策將在2021完結？","createTime":"2021-02-24T08:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T12:13:35.000Z","uid":243259,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1d4022b254343e5049138d3616333c2fef3fe6","tid":2421034,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:48:51.000Z","msg":"眾所鳩知 香港政府收入 大多數嚟自賣地<br />\n即係高地價政策<br />\n即使政府極力否認 但例如安峯 麵粉價都1萬4蚊 麵包賣2萬幾蚊 亦無可口非<br />\n<br />\n香港一直樓價高企嘅原因 <br />\n部份係源自高地價政策<br />\n長久以來政府依賴收入單一稅收 <br />\n稅制簡單 <br />\n唯一嘅解決方法 就係加稅/加稅項<br />\n<br />\n2021年財報 全方位增加稅收 <br />\n但賣地卻甚少著墨<br />\n是代表高地價政策嘅終結嗎？麵包可以減價？港樓還會gogogo?"},{"pid":"d1ca7be08318ded9bf1a1a54fccf022c55b4d8ce","tid":2421034,"uid":84046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"支講到明樓價令到人反"},{"pid":"3de704e4ac3147f47648145413099a6bc62c7d7d","tid":2421034,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"近日財爺嘅言論 愈來愈說明高地價政策已經完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b4a5a97e84c66b99404c9988cebcbdb80c70d7","tid":2421034,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de704e4ac3147f47648145413099a6bc62c7d7d","tid":2421034,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"近日財爺嘅言論 愈來愈說明高地價政策已經完結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:59:00.000Z","msg":"變做收呼吸稅一樣仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77add4c87b9f68c06244f484f873f65678d40e5","tid":2421034,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b4a5a97e84c66b99404c9988cebcbdb80c70d7","tid":2421034,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de704e4ac3147f47648145413099a6bc62c7d7d","tid":2421034,"uid":243259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"近日財爺嘅言論 愈來愈說明高地價政策已經完結<img src=